[Swapping Left-Ctrl with CapsLock]
1. On terminal: setxkbmap -option caps:escape
2. Modifying the file: sudo nvim /etc/default/keyboard

Check list available for xkb: grep "compose:" /usr/share/X11/xkb/rules/base.lst

VSCode에서 작동오류 고치는 법
VSCode에서 Setting으로 가서
"keyboard.dispatch": "keyCode" and restart VS Code
